title: Main Morg lf Mate
body:
Hey guys, I am looking for a good mate to get high into Ranked games.
I am actually a silver player but I know that I can get better.
I dont want rager or quitter, I want a good mate that also tells me what I am doing wrong and is patient with me.

My Name ingame is "Corzelius"
and this is my battlelog: http://euw.op.gg/summoner/userName=Corzelius
Cya guys

replies.body: you should probably tell people which lane you play since morg is viable for muiltiple lanes
